title: InterVention Recruitment
body:
Hey Guys, 
If you're a Jungler and are looking to join a competitive team for Ranked 5v5, then message me with some details. At the moment I am scouting for players who are serious and are keen to do Tournaments Australia Wide.

replies.body:
Hey mate, had a look at your match history, its obvious you main jungle and do it well. If you are interested and want to join, play a few matches with us on the weekend. Ill add you on League and if you're comfortable, join our skype call for communication. If you do well and have good synergy with the team, we will be excited to have you join. 

-GodzillaTheNinja (Team Manager and Support)

hey add me if you need a jungler or support, both my main roles I play! :)

IG: skunken
I can pull a mean 360 YY No-scope off the top Highrise. HMU, my intervention has Tiger Camo. I never Headshot Boosted I swear it.
